* (right) Landslide Creek
** (right) Cascade Creek
* (right) Section Thirteen Creek
* (right) Six Tile Creek

== Drainage basin ==
The Jordan River system drains all or portions of the following cities, villages and townships:
* Antrim County
** Echo Township
** Chestonia Township
** Jordan Township
** Star Township
** Warner Township
* Charlevoix County
** Boyne Valley Township
** East Jordan
** South Arm Township
** Wilson Township

