<doc id="480593" wikidata="Q17503171" url="?curid=480593" title="Abercrombie Plan">
<text>Abercrombie Plan may refer to any one of a number of urban planning proposals written or co-written by Sir Leslie Patrick Abercrombie, including:

*&quot;County of London Plan&quot; (1943, with John Henry Forshaw)
*&quot;Greater London Plan&quot; (1944)
*&quot;A Plan for the City &amp; County of Kingston upon Hull&quot; (1945, with Sir Edwin Lutyens)
* Abercrombie Plan (Edinburgh) a plan for Edinburgh 
* &quot;A Plan for Plymouth&quot; (1943)

